ISLAMABAD, Apr 7 (APP):President Dr Arif Alvi Tuesday administered oath to Syed Fakhar Imam as Federal Minister for National Food Security in a ceremony held at the Aiwan-e-Sadr.
Previously, Syed Fakhar Imam had also served as speaker of the National Assembly and had the experience of a member of the federal cabinet twice.
